# Block access to sensitive files (拡張子ベースで広く拒否。.bak/.sql/.log 等も対象)
<FilesMatch "(?i)(^\.env|^service-account\.json|\.(bak|sql|log|ini|sh)$|\.json\.bak)">
    Require all denied
</FilesMatch>

# ディレクトリ一覧表示の禁止
Options -Indexes

# Error handling
ErrorDocument 404 /404.php

# 静的アセットのブラウザキャッシュ（CSS/JSは ?v=filemtime でバスティング済みのため長期間でOK）
<IfModule mod_expires.c>
    ExpiresActive On
    ExpiresByType image/jpeg "access plus 30 days"
    ExpiresByType image/png "access plus 30 days"
    ExpiresByType image/gif "access plus 30 days"
    ExpiresByType image/webp "access plus 30 days"
    ExpiresByType image/x-icon "access plus 30 days"
    ExpiresByType text/css "access plus 30 days"
    ExpiresByType application/javascript "access plus 30 days"
    ExpiresByType font/woff2 "access plus 365 days"
</IfModule>

# Redirect old URLs to new locations
RewriteEngine On
RewriteBase /

# sitemap.xml はブログ記事を含めて動的生成
RewriteRule ^sitemap\.xml$ sitemap.php [L]

# Redirect /about-us to home
RewriteRule ^about-us/?$ / [R=301,L]

# Redirect /contact to home contact section
RewriteRule ^contact/?$ /#contact [R=301,NE,L]

# Redirect /activity to domestic
RewriteRule ^activity/?$ /activity_domestic.php [R=301,L]

# Redirect /gv /jv to proper pages
RewriteRule ^gv/?$ /activity_gv.php [R=301,L]
RewriteRule ^jv/?$ /activity_jv.php [R=301,L]
RewriteRule ^domestic/?$ /activity_domestic.php [R=301,L]

# Redirect /member to dashboard
RewriteRule ^member/?$ /dashboard.php [R=301,L]

# Old Japanese URLs
RewriteRule ^%E3%83%AC%E3%82%AF%E3%83%AA%E3%82%A8%E3%83%BC%E3%82%B7%E3%83%A7%E3%83%B3/?$ / [R=301,L]
RewriteRule ^jcc/?$ / [R=301,L]
RewriteRule ^%E9%80%9A%E5%B8%B8mtg/?$ /activity_mtg.php [R=301,L]
RewriteRule ^%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%85%E6%B4%BE%E9%81%A3/?$ /activity_domestic.php [R=301,L]
